description:
&lt;p&gt;“Are you an enthusiastic, forward thinking nurse who can deliver high quality nursing care to improve the physical, mental and psycho-social wellbeing of older people?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for a staff nurse to join our forward thinking, dynamic and supportive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Career progression and staff development is the key to growing our successful teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beechdale at the Dales , Calderdale Royal Infirmary, Halifax and Ward 19, Priestley Unit, Dewsbury are Older Peoples inpatient wards which have a positive working reputation &amp; we pride ourselves on being a fantastic place to work, providing high standards of care. The evidence is clear in the positive feedback that we receive from service users, their families and from students on University placements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to join our exciting, friendly team please contact us. You can speak to any of the managers &amp; arrange a visit. We would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kim Osborn, Janice Bryson and Helen Dowd”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All shortlisted candidates will be invited in dial into a Skype or Microsoft Teams interview, scheduled to take place on: Thursday 26th November and/or Saturday 28th November.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
